      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 247,
      "message": "Hi\n\nCould you tell me how user will know what to set here? Init flag usually is executed as first step in ONAP so after that user have repo synchronized. If you want to have this as parameter we need to introduce new flag to this script. Also I suggest to keep this path as default value.",
