    {
      "id": "545efa0f_4e4e3429",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/robot/demo-k8s.sh",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 247,
      "message": "Okay, understood. If this script scope is primarily for ONAP testcase prep, then fine with defaulting the path. For supporting MOD helm flows (dcaemod testcase) though, need also other oom/common charts (such as common/repositoryGenerator/readinessCheck/postgres) to be loaded into registry. \nHence oom/kubernetes/common load should be added into this script (or change default to pick all charts under oom/kubernetes - this will allow other onap components also be deployed on-demand)",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 93,
        "name": "Vijay Venkatesh Kumar",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "vijayv81@gmail.com",
        "username": "vv770d"
